<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.9">
<l>ōti nāmam kuḷittuc citaṉṉā loḷimāmalarp</l>
<l>pātam nāḷum paṇivōm namakkē nalamātaliṉ</l>
<l>ātu tārā ṉeṉilun tarumaṉ ṟiyumaṉparāyp</l>
<l>pōtum mātē toḻutu mavaṉmaṉ ṉupullāṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Chanting his names [and] bathing, we bow every day with our heads</l>
<l>At his lustrous, dark flower[-like] feet, because the pleasure is only for us!</l>
<l>Even if he never gives us anything, [he] gives [us this]. Besides, Lady,</l>
<l>[His] being [our] beloved is enough. We will worship in Pullāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">where he abides.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
